---
// StatsSection - 公司概览与核心数据展示
---

<section class="stats-section animate-fade-up">
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-100">SHANDONG YONGAN CONSTRUCTION MACHINERY GROUP CO., LTD</h2>
    <p class="intro animate-fade-up animate-delay-200">Shandong Yongan Construction Machinery Group was founded in 2001, the company is headquartered in Jinan City, Shandong Province, its subsidiaries 6, is a research and development, production, sales, service, leasing in one of the professional construction machinery manufacturers and service providers.</p>
    <p class="intro animate-fade-up animate-delay-300">The company has a modern production and service base, covers an area of more than 60,000 square meters, the existing staff of more than 500 people, equipped with the international leading level of production equipment and technical force, from raw material procurement to product assembly, every link strictly follow the international quality management system standards, to ensure...</p>

    <div class="stats-row animate-fade-up animate-delay-400">
      <div class="stat-item animate-scale-up animate-delay-500">
        <div class="stat-value counter-number" data-count="2001">2001</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Incorporation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item animate-scale-up animate-delay-600">
        <div class="stat-value counter-number" data-count="60000">60000</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Floor space</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item animate-scale-up animate-delay-700">
        <div class="stat-value counter-number" data-count="120">120+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Exporting country</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item animate-scale-up animate-delay-800">
        <div class="stat-value counter-number" data-count="500">500+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Have employees</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/about" class="view-all-btn animate-fade-up animate-delay-900">View all →</a>
    <div style="width: 100%; position: absolute;display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-12">
        <!-- High Quality -->
        <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center card-item card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-1000">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">High quality</h3>
          <p>Ensure to provide customers with high quality, high performance, high reliability of construction machinery products</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Diversified Demand -->
        <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center card-item card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-1100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Diversified demand</h3>
          <p>Offering versatile solutions tailored to various applications.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Reduce Cost -->
        <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center card-item card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-1200">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Reduce cost</h3>
          <p>Delivering efficient and cost-effective solutions for our customers</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Perfect Service -->
        <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center card-item card-hover-animate animate-fade-up animate-delay-1300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Perfect service</h3>
          <p>Ensuring comprehensive support and customer satisfaction at every step</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.stats-section {
  position: relative;
  background: url('/company-bg.webp') center/cover no-repeat;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 8rem 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 20rem;
}
.stats-section .overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}
.stats-section .container {
  position: relative;
  max-width: 1460px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
  padding-bottom: 10rem;
}
.stats-section h2 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.stats-section .intro {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}
.stats-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 4rem;
  margin: 3rem 0;
}
.stat-item {
  text-align: center;
}
.stat-value {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
}
.stat-label {
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 1rem;
}
.view-all-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 2rem;
  color: #fff;
  border: 2px solid #fff;
  padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}
.view-all-btn:hover {
  background: #fff;
  color: #000;
}
.stats-section .card-item {
  width: 27rem;
  height: 30rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 2rem;
}
@media (max-width: 1023px) {
  .stats-section {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0rem;
  }
  .stats-section .container{
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .stats-row {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .stat-item {
    flex: 1 1 45%;
  }
  .stats-section .container > div[style*="position: absolute"] {
    position: static !important;
    display: block !important;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }
  .stats-section .grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    gap: 1rem !important;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .stats-section .card-item {
    width: 100% !important;
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto !important;
    margin: 1rem auto;
    font-size: 1.5rem !important;
  }
}
</style> 